Definitions

- Module: a collection of Dictu files capable of being imported into Dictu code
  - Version
  - Author
  - Dependencies
  - Author

- Install directory: directory where all modules will be installed
  - ~/.dictu/modules
  - Modules will be installed in their own directory within this top level modules directory
  
- Module Configuration File
  - JSON format with the following fields:
    - Name
    - License
    - Version
    - Maintainers
      - Name
      - Email
    - Dependencies
      - Name
      - Version

- Formats
  - tar, tar.gz, zip?
  - directory?
  
- HTTP Retrieval?

- Further Considerations
  - Compiler Adjustments
    - Upon import, search ~/.dictu/modules/ for any matching modules
